            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Cruise Mode drafts a 1,500-word article in 5 minutes</li>
                <li>Keyword planner + optimiser + AI writer bundled</li>
