                <li>Schedules content on a queue — set and forget</li>
                <li>Internal-linking automation across the library</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Pure automation — minimal editorial guardrails</li>
                <li>Article quality varies by niche</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
